{"tid":1211274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(請推）今日我有去，聽日都會去","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:52.000Z","uid":141784,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"122433c3a00587984e510488a7d5f691058da5cb","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">整合今天：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日我係現場 唔係係前線 企係隧道到 係就四點既情況下 警方施放催淚彈<br />\n我唔係負責衝 淨係係傳物資個個位都已經覺得皮膚刺痛 見到好多人其實想守 但係要退後俾前面既人退後 我地唔係企前線都感覺到有野 前面既人呢？<br />\n唔係想退 係根本唔知前面咩環境 唔退後佢地咪要被迫食曬？於是越退越後 退到去太古商場個邊<br />\n<br />\n見到大家都好齊心 要退就一齊退 讓路 傳物資<br />\n到後面都見到好多人收工有掃物資過物資站</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家以為流會就好足夠？錯！我地宜家只係開始，我地既目的係要佢地徹回修例<br />\n<br />\n今日我地其實並無成功到 前線人員都係血肉之軀 佢以身開路俾我地衝入立法院 受槍彈 受警棍 憑咩佢地要做開荒牛？因為佢地深信 佢地有後盾 明白唔係個個市民都肯上街都肯罷工 但係麻煩大家見到有人俾狗拉俾狗拖 麻煩拉返佢返黎 唔好覺得自己既力量好薄弱 我地勇士少一個就少好多 <br />\n<br />\n「你未必夠膽衝 但係你可以幫手袋裝備 有需要就傳」<br />\n要打卡既唔該留係屋企 宜家係打仗 唔係講玩<br />\n<br />\n唔好再分化咩和理非同要衝 <br />\n我地槍頭要對外 今日係現場見到冇共識 前線人員又冇凝聚力 同開始失望真係好心痛</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地聽日既目標<br />\n裝備上既差異令我地明白 硬碰硬唔係冇可能 不過只會有更多人白白犧牲<br />\n罷工唔係咁多人夠膽同公司講 既然係咁 我地就要轉戰場<br />\n聽日隧道同港鐵就係我地既戰場！要癱瘓香港既經濟活動！<br />\n<br />\n多你一個 其實好多！<br />\n香港人加油！</span>"},{"pid":"868c4c710e302f70010c5a3700ade29e66fb657a","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923bf8b8fc5f4c963c18c68310324d7cf7b6195f","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ee069121c1d1c1128610a48a4921a6b5a9f663","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bad9541dc6461b6bd22b08dac9792c3253caa58","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d328034b0673703581570cbefc315926c9e6cd7","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4531738a326b0a3c78c833eeb29f34b747a3da52","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08a43944a07f4931d0c0965f9e3fa1f2553a22e","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4430225ef9cdfa9e712a56b1544a4e901bb56d6c","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7457501329d675d3ca33e92d7031a82e6350638","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7ae24c2fecba13098c1dfdd9b8d79997784f14","tid":1211274,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}